Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you takin' us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, young 'uns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There? Where? What?\NI don't even know what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders, welcome\Nto your new clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't thank me all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This was my clubhouse when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure it hasn't been used in a while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's empty and on a secluded\Nprivate part of the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It just needs a little, uh... TLC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,TLC as in Tender Loving Care\Nor Totally Lost Cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack! We're supposed to turn\Nthis into our new clubhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe y'all will get your cutie marks\Nwhen you discover your talent for...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...house cleanin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Hi, Scootaloo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Back already? You're 'mazin' on that scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Wow, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I've fixed the broken shutters, sanded off\Nthe splinters, rebuilt the roof, painted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool. What's Sweetie Belle up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the Cutie Mark Crusaders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...never stop the journey...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you we could find her\Nby followin' her totally awesome voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sweet tune you're singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I was just working on our new\NCutie Mark Crusaders theme song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,COOL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've only come up with one part...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all say that you will get your mark{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the time is really right{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you know just what you're supposed to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}AND YOUR TALENT COMES TO LIGHT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... I'll be, Cutie Mark Crusaders.\NYou've done one fine job with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we have a real life clubhouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And a map of Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And a Cutie Mark Crusaders theme song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Theme song?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna go out in the world\Nand discover our talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A new adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And earn our cutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave no stone unturned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No mountain unclimbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No meal uncooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No sock unwarmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well okay then! Sounds like you have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave no apple unpicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See y'all later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we ready to get our cutie marks, ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we sure aren't gettin'\Nour cutie marks for bein' librarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I should think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls, I think you're going\Nabout this the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to do things\Nin areas you're not familiar with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...why not try doing things\Nin areas that you already like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have the perfect place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Showcase your talents..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"...for all to see..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Perform in the Ponyville school talent show."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be all sorts of awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Best dramatic performance,\Nbest comedy act, best magic act...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you can find your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This *would* be the perfect place\Nto discover our talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jugglin'!\N-Acting!\N-Magic tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Square dancin'!\N-Tightrope walking!\N-Tiger taming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My little ponies! You're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the things you already enjoy doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about what you're already good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! We can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Sure we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever we do, we'll do it as...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...The Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle! I told you not to touch my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back with my supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just borrowing them for the talent show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, sis. I promise we'll bring them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Breezy.\NWe'll return the fan to you real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we need this fan for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so that's six wooden planks,\N4 by 8 plywood, a box of nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...four cans of paint and four brushes.\NAnything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Instructions on how to use six wooden\Nplanks, 4 by 8 plywood, a box of nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...four cans of paint and four brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ghost, Goblins and Ghoulish Figures"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good heavens, girls.\NWhat do you need a book like this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see. Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give it back as soon as we're done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think they're up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea and I don't know if\NI should be excited or scared to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we're doin' this as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... so what are we doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A super awesome dramatic song\Nfor the talent show, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! With super-cool scenery.\NAnd amazing costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And mind-blowin' dance moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, I think you should be a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way I'm singing in front of a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight said to do something we like to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to be like my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's a designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then. You can do\Nthe costumes and the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Scootaloo, you're great\Nin maneuvers on your scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should do the choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, all those dance moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I'd rather sing a wicked rock ballad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come up with\Nthe dance routine, Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not much of a dancer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I do like Kung-fu.\NThat's kinda like dancin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled! Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One... two... three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, Apple Bloom! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I feel like I have four left feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even spin right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. You just gotta keep your head\Nforward until very the last minute. Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Easy-peasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just gotta practice a bunch, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That does look easy. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight the fight, walk the walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk the talk, eat a... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...food like a celery stalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never come up with anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Never, never, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Scoot! How's the song going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Sounds serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just no good at lyrics.\NComing up with words is, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it can't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With our cutie marks we'll rock Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We use our stomachs to... digestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... These are... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...good, but... How about after\N"We fight the fight"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is nothing that we fear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll have to figure out what we'll do next{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Till our cutie marks are here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just come up with that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'm totally using that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, FIVE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the spin coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll gotta just stick to punches and kicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, ponies only have four legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be a designer like my sister Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you use the dress form?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll help you with your patterns and help\Nyou put all the pieces in the right places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what that's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... maybe you should also clean\Nyour paintbrush between each color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was wondering why\Nall the colors looked like mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not using power tools, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The talent show is just around the corner.\NI wonder how the fillies are doin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh! Sorry, Scootaloo.\N-That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Oops! Sorry, Scootaloo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ouch!\N-Oh, my bad, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sing the chorus again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gosh. Sure wasn't expectin' that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that sounded pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. You think we're ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready as we'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Did you see us practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? How do we do? How do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Speechless! See, girls?\NI told you that's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna leave them speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,YAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Speechless" is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...and on the count of three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...this rabbit will disappear and something\Ntasty will reappear in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A one, a two and a three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Snails, where are the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,SNAILS!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, how about a round of applause\Nfor the S&S magic act?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for our next act we have Sunny Days and\NPeachy Pie reciting their favorite poem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...on rollerskates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Break a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle! What a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. You see, in the theater\Nit's considered bad luck to say "good luck".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say "break a leg" instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My little ponies! How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You're gonna be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, just stick to what you know best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear you sing, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everypony always\Nthink I'm gonna sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight Sparkle,\NI'm the main singer tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the main dancer. Hai-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm in charge of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And sets and props. How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, girls? Are you sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie Mark Crusaders, you're on next.\NBreak a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Break a le...\N-Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, here are three little ponies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ready to sing for this crowd{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen up cause here's our story{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna sing it VERY LOUD!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you're a younger pony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And your flank is very bare{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feels like the sun will never come{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When your cutie mark's not there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the three of us fight the fight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is nothing that we fear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll have to figure out what we'll do next{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Till our cutie marks are here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the Cutie Mark Crusaders{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a quest to find out who we are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we will never stop the journey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not until we have our cutie marks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all say that you'll get your mark{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the time is really right{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you know just what you're supposed to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And your talent comes to light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's not as easy as it sounds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that waiting's hard to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we test our talents everywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until our face is blue{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the Cutie Mark Crusaders{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a quest to find out who we are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we will never stop the journey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not until we have our cutie marks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the Cutie Mark Crusaders{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a quest to find out who we are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we will never stop the journey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not until we have our cutie marks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That did not go as well as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they're laughin' at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back on stage, girls. It's time for the awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Back on stage? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll just laugh some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now girls, let's be good sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a great effort. You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for all\Nour talented fillies and colts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first award goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Snips and Snails for best magic act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mine's at least shinier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, mine's bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, well... Well, mine is, uh... heavier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The next award goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunny Days and Peachy Pie\Nfor best dramatic performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the last award\Nof the night goes to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For best comedy act.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it? We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew our act was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what would be the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we won *and* we got our cutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, ponies! Job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't sound too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked really hard and won a prize\Nbut we still don't have our cutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is the prize we really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But we think we know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Tell me. I'd love to make\Na special report to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe we were trying too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of forcing ourselves to\Ndo something that's not meant for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We each should be embracing our true talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Comedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see our award? Weren't we funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One day... One day...
